<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('./layouts/head'); -%>
</head>
<body>
    <% if (isAuthenticated && userRole==='admin') { %>
        <header id="header">
          <%- include('./layouts/header'); -%>
        </header>
    <% } %>

  <section class="section" id="showcase">
      <div class="container has-text-centered">
          <h1 class="title is-1">Advanced GIS Solutions</h1>
          <p class="subtitle is-4">Transform your geospatial data management with our comprehensive suite of tools</p>
          <a href="#" class="button is-primary is-medium">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
          <div class="columns is-multiline">
              <div class="column is-one-third">
                  <div class="box">
                      <h2 class="title is-4">3D Mapping with Cesium</h2>
                      <p>MGIS 3D-Planner utilizes <a href="https://cesium.com/" target="_blank">CesiumJS</a> for advanced 3D visualization, allowing you to:</p>
                      <ul>
                          <li>Render 3D Tiles for large-scale geospatial datasets.</li>
                          <li>Measure distances and areas directly on the map.</li>
                          <li>Visualize real-world terrains and integrate Cesium Ion assets.</li>
                          <li>Create, edit, and save 3D maps for planning and analysis.</li>
                      </ul>
                      <p>With Cesium's powerful engine, you can bring your geospatial data to life, enhancing planning and decision-making processes.</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="column is-one-third">
                  <div class="box">
                      <h2 class="title is-4">QGIS-Server Manager</h2>
                      <p>QGIS-Server Manager is a cutting-edge application designed to simplify the administration of <a href="https://qgis.org" target="_blank">QGIS Server</a>. It offers a user-friendly interface to:</p>
                      <ul>
                          <li>Seamlessly manage WMS, WFS, and WMTS projects.</li>
                          <li>Upload and configure layers, styles, and services efficiently.</li>
                          <li>Optimize map performance for high-demand environments.</li>
                          <li>Enable secure and collaborative sharing of geospatial data.</li>
                      </ul>
                      <p>Stay tuned for more updates and detailed information about QGIS-Server Manager.</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="column is-one-third">
                  <div class="box">
                      <h2 class="title is-4">Origo Map Plus</h2>
                      <p>Origo Map Plus is an intuitive application tailored for the efficient management of <a href="https://origo-map.github.io/" target="_blank">Origo maps</a>. Designed to eliminate the need for coding, it empowers users to:</p>
                      <ul>
                          <li>Edit and update Origo maps and configurations effortlessly.</li>
                          <li>Implement real-time map adjustments for immediate results.</li>
                          <li>Integrate seamlessly with other GIS tools and workflows.</li>
                          <li>Enhance productivity with a streamlined map management process.</li>
                      </ul>
                      <p>Detailed information and updates on Origo Map Plus will be available soon.</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
          <div class="content has-text-centered">
              <h2 class="title is-3">Contact Us</h2>
              <p>We offer commercial consulting on MGIS 3D-Planner and other open source applications like QGIS Server, GeoServer, GeoWebCache, PostGIS, 3D Cesium, and more.</p>
              <p>If you have any questions or need further information, feel free to reach out to us:</p>
              <p>Email: <a href="mailto:abel.gonzalez@mundogis.eu">abel.gonzalez@mundogis.eu</a></p>
              <p>Website: <a href="https://mundogis.eu/?page_id=11" target="_blank">Contact Us</a></p>
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
      <div class="content has-text-centered">
          <p>MundoGIS &copy; 2024</p>
      </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
